00:43:14,240 --> 00:43:15,400
[laughs]

995
00:43:15,480 --> 00:43:17,640
Yes, but I want to be different
from all men.

996
00:43:17,720 --> 00:43:18,960
In what way?

997
00:43:19,040 --> 00:43:21,640
An A-plus partner

998
00:43:21,720 --> 00:43:23,000
looks like me.

999
00:43:23,080 --> 00:43:24,240
[laughs]

1000
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:26,200
- [laughs]
- [clears throat]

1001
00:43:26,800 --> 00:43:29,056
- I'm saying it because it's accurate, Mum.
- Yeah. [laughs]

1002
00:43:29,080 --> 00:43:30,280
Far-out, Mike.

1003
00:43:30,960 --> 00:43:32,440
- And...
- He's cute.

1004
00:43:32,520 --> 00:43:34,240
...when I do get married in the future,

