00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:37,960
not only will my wife be
my most crowning achievement, but also,

1006
00:43:38,360 --> 00:43:41,880
I've actually envisioned
a lot of family members in the future

1007
00:43:41,960 --> 00:43:44,360
saying this...
these words to my wife af...

1008
00:43:44,840 --> 00:43:45,760
after my passing.

1009
00:43:45,840 --> 00:43:47,920
- What the hell?
- After your passing?

1010
00:43:48,000 --> 00:43:49,040
[scoffs]

1011
00:43:49,120 --> 00:43:50,320
"Being your husband...

1012
00:43:51,160 --> 00:43:53,280
nothing made that man any happier."

1013
00:43:53,360 --> 00:43:54,720
- [laughs]
- [father] Mate...

1014
00:43:54,800 --> 00:43:57,376
- You're thinking too far ahead, mate.
- Dad, I always think ahead.

1015
00:43:57,400 --> 00:44:00,080
- [laughs]
- [mother] Yeah, but that's a bit too far.

1016
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,240
Excuse me, everyone.
