1017
00:44:04,320 --> 00:44:05,496
- for the date.
- [mother] Okay.

1018
00:44:05,520 --> 00:44:06,520
Thank you.

1019
00:44:08,600 --> 00:44:10,840
- So cute.
- [footsteps departing]

1020
00:44:12,560 --> 00:44:13,600
[Michael] Okay, which one?

1021
00:44:13,680 --> 00:44:14,680
[inhales]

1022
00:44:18,080 --> 00:44:19,080
Ah-ha!

1023
00:44:24,520 --> 00:44:25,800
[father] Don't wanna be late!

1024
00:44:25,880 --> 00:44:27,080
I know, I'm coming.

1025
00:44:28,880 --> 00:44:30,480
[mother] Don't forget the rose.

1026
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:33,360
- I won't forget that either, Mum.
- [mother] Okay.

1027
00:44:33,440 --> 00:44:35,336
- No problem.
- [father] Don't forget your wallet.

1028
00:44:35,360 --> 00:44:37,920
- [father laughs]
- Nope. I never forget that, either.

1029
00:44:39,000 --> 00:44:40,800
- [mother laughs]
- My... My hair comb.

1030
00:44:41,320 --> 00:44:43,560
Um, just... Just bear with me
for a couple of minutes.

1031
00:44:43,640 --> 00:44:46,040
- We'll be there, we'll be there!
- [father laughs]

1032
00:44:46,120 --> 00:44:47,320
[mother] It's all right, Mike.

1033
00:44:50,560 --> 00:44:51,560
Ready.

1034
00:44:51,640 --> 00:44:52,896
- [mother] Okay.
- [father] Ready?

1035
00:44:52,920 --> 00:44:54,160
Yep, ready.

1036
00:44:54,240 --> 00:44:55,240
Good stuff.

1037
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:57,320
All right, well, all the best, Michael.

1038
00:44:57,400 --> 00:44:58,440
- Good luck.
- Thanks, Dad.

1039
00:44:58,840 --> 00:44:59,840
Thank you.

1040
00:45:00,640 --> 00:45:02,080
Take care, Dad.

1041
00:45:02,160 --> 00:45:03,600
[father] Good. Now get outta here.

1042
00:45:03,680 --> 00:45:05,936
- Yep, see ya, Dad.
- [father] Nice flower, by the way, too.

1043
00:45:05,960 --> 00:45:08,296
- [Michael] See ya.
- [mother] Remember your brother's advice.

1044
00:45:08,320 --> 00:45:09,560
[Michael] Got it! Got it.

1045
00:45:09,640 --> 00:45:10,760
[birds squawking]

1046
00:45:15,440 --> 00:45:17,080
- Ah, thank you.
- You're welcome.

1047
00:45:17,160 --> 00:45:19,040
- Thank you.
- Would you like some table water?

1048
00:45:19,120 --> 00:45:20,720
Uh, yes please, thank... thank...

1049
00:45:20,800 --> 00:45:21,880
Please and thank you.

1050
00:45:28,640 --> 00:45:29,640
[exhales]

1051
00:45:31,600 --> 00:45:32,600
[man] You all right?

